\p{We recall a few easy consequences of the cubes detect continuity and
#{\Delta^1} detects connectivity axioms.}

\agda{
opaque
  cubes-separate : family-separates в–Ў^_
  cubes-separate = family-separatesвҶҗdetects-continuity в–Ў^_ cubes-detect-cont

  cubes-separate'
    : вҲҖ {@вҷӯ рқ“Ө рқ“Ҙ} (@вҷӯ fa : Arrow рқ“Ө рқ“Ҙ) (let @вҷӯ f = Arrow.f fa)
      вҶ’ @вҷӯ ((вҲҖ {@вҷӯ n} вҶ’ is-equiv (вҷӯ-map (postcomp (в–Ў^ n) f))))
      вҶ’ is-equiv f
  cubes-separate' fa eq
    = cubes-separate
        fa
        (tgt-is-equivвҶҗArrow-equiv (amap , amap-is-equiv) (eq {0}))
        eq where
    open Arrow fa
    amap : Arrow-map (вҷӯ-map (postcomp (в–Ў^ 0) f)) (вҷӯ-map f)
    amap .Arrow-О .top = вҷӯ-map (ev (mk-lift tt))
    amap .Arrow-О .bot = вҷӯ-map (ev (mk-lift tt))
    amap .Arrow-О .comm (modвҷӯ f) = refl

    amap-is-equiv : is-Arrow-equiv amap
    amap-is-equiv .fst = вҷӯ-map-is-equiv (sing-ev-is-equiv global-funext single!)
    amap-is-equiv .snd = вҷӯ-map-is-equiv (sing-ev-is-equiv global-funext single!)
}

\subtree[stt-00AS]{
\title{There is a universe of amazingly covariant types}
\taxon{Construction}

\p{Assuming that the interval is [tiny](Synthetic.Tiny), there is a universe of
\em{amazingly covariant types}, which weakly classify the left fibrations.
We denote it #{\mathcal{S}}.}

\proof{
\p{Since being covariant (or equivalently being a left fibration), is
a [#{\Delta^1}-relative class of maps](stt-00K1). By the machinery
developed for [amazing right adjoints](stt-00AA), we can construct a universe
which classifies this class.
}
}

\agda{
is-covariant-is-relative : is-relative-fam О”В№ is-covariant
is-covariant-is-relative {B = A} P = (fwd , bwd) where
  fwd : is-covariant P вҶ’ (x : О”В№ вҶ’ A) вҶ’ is-covariant (P вҲҳ x)
  fwd cov f h = cov (f вҲҳ h)

  bwd : ((x : О”В№ вҶ’ A) вҶ’ is-covariant (P вҲҳ x)) вҶ’ is-covariant P
  bwd cov h xвӮҖ = cov h id xвӮҖ

open DependentвҲҡ О”В№ вҲҡ вҲҡОө is-tiny-str
               public
open AmazinglyFibrant О”В№ вҲҡ вҲҡОө is-tiny-str
               is-covariant is-covariant-is-prop is-covariant-is-relative
               public
  renaming (is-afib to is-acov;
            UFib to Space;
            UFibвҲҷ to SpaceвҲҷ;
            UFib-ПҖ-is-fib to Space-ПҖ-is-covariant)
}
}

\subtree[stt-00AU]{
\title{The objects of #{\mathcal{S}} are groupoids}
\taxon{Theorem}

\p{If #{A :^\flat \UU} is a groupoid, then #{A} is amazing covariant and so
factors through #{\mathcal{S}}.}

\agda{
groupoids-in-Space : вҲҖ {@вҷӯ рқ“Ө} (@вҷӯ A : Type рқ“Ө) вҶ’ @вҷӯ is-О”В№-discrete A вҶ’ is-acov A
groupoids-in-Space A О”В№-discrete
  = Оөвҷӯ (liftFib .fst
         (modвҷӯ (is-covariantвҮ”is-left-fibration
                 (О» _ вҶ’ A) .snd
                   (is-orthogonalвҮ”orthogonal-! .snd
                     (is-leftвҶҗis-О”В№-discrete
                       (Null-globally-ОЈ-closed
                         (рқҹҷ-is-О”В№-discrete)
                         (О» _ вҶ’ О”В№-discrete)) tt))))) tt
}
}

\subtree[stt-00L2]{
\title{Closure properties of amazing covariance}
\taxon{Theorem}

\p{The universe of amazingly covariant types is closed under
#{\times, \Sigma} and #{=}.
}

\proof{
\p{The proof strategy for all of the results are the same, in general we may
reduce the problem to the analogous [closure conditions for covariant
families](Synthetic.Categories.CovariantClosure).}

\p{We provide the proof for closure under equality as an example. Let #{\Gamma}
be the type #{\Sigma_{A : \mathcal{S}} (A \times A)}, and #{\sigma} the map
#{\Gamma \to \Type} defined as #{(A,a,b) \mapsto a = b}. We need to show that
#{\Pi_{x : \Gamma} \textsf{is-Acov}(\sigma x)}, which by unfolding the definition
of amazing covariance is just
#{\Pi_{x : \Gamma} \sqrt{\textsf{is-covariant}}(\sigma x)}, but by naturality
of the #{\sqrt[I]{{-}}} former, this is the same as
#{\Pi_{x : \Gamma} \sqrt{\textsf{is-covariant} \circ \sigma_*}(x)}. We may
use the universal property of #{\sqrt{-}} so that it suffices to give an
element #{\Pi_{x : \Gamma^{\Delta^1}} \textsf{is-covariant}(\sigma_* \circ x)}.
}

\p{Now we have dealt with the root former, we may proceed less formally. We have
a map #{A : \Delta^1 \to \mathcal{S}}, which means #{A} is a covariant family of
types over #{\Delta^1}, and a pair of sections #{a\ b : \Pi_{\Delta^1} A},
we want to show #{i \mapsto a_i = b_i} is covariant, which [follows by general
closure properties of orthogonality](stt-00KG).}
}


\agda{
opaque
  Г—-is-acov
    : вҲҖ {@вҷӯ рқ“Ө рқ“Ҙ} {A : Type рқ“Ө} {B : Type рқ“Ҙ}
      вҶ’ is-acov A вҶ’ is-acov B вҶ’ is-acov (A Г— B)
  Г—-is-acov {рқ“Ө} {рқ“Ҙ} a b = need ((mk-ufib _ a) , (mk-ufib _ b)) where
    open Space
    @вҷӯ П• : (x : О”В№ вҶ’ Space рқ“Ө Г— Space рқ“Ҙ)
         вҶ’ is-covariant (О» iВ вҶ’ x i .fst .Carrier Г— x i .snd .Carrier)
    П• О“ = Г—-is-covariant
               {P = Carrier вҲҳ fst вҲҳ О“}
               {Q = Carrier вҲҳ snd вҲҳ О“}
               (UFib-is-fib (fst вҲҳ О“))
               (UFib-is-fib (snd вҲҳ О“))

    П•МӮ : О  (Space рқ“Ө Г— Space рқ“Ҙ)
              (вҲҡбөҲ (О» g вҶ’ is-covariant (О» i вҶ’ g i .fst .Carrier Г— g i .snd .Carrier)))
    П•МӮ = Оөвҷӯ (rintro (modвҷӯ П•))

    need : (О“ : Space рқ“Ө Г— Space рқ“Ҙ) вҶ’ (is-acov (О“ .fst .Carrier Г— О“ .snd .Carrier))
    need g = вҲҡбөҲ-naturalityвҶҗ _ _ _ (П•МӮ g)

instance
  Г—-Is-acov
    : вҲҖ {@вҷӯ рқ“Ө рқ“Ҙ} {A : Type рқ“Ө} {B : Type рқ“Ҙ}
        вҰғ _ : is-acov A вҰ„ вҰғ _ : is-acov B вҰ„
      вҶ’ is-acov (A Г— B)
  Г—-Is-acov = Г—-is-acov auto! auto!

opaque
  ОЈ-is-acov
    : вҲҖ {@вҷӯ рқ“Ө рқ“Ҙ} {A : Type рқ“Ө} {B : A вҶ’ Type рқ“Ҙ}
      вҶ’ is-acov A вҶ’ (вҲҖ a вҶ’ is-acov (B a)) вҶ’ is-acov (ОЈ A B)
  ОЈ-is-acov {рқ“Ө} {рқ“Ҙ} a b = need ((mk-ufib _ a) , (О» i вҶ’ mk-ufib _ (b i))) where
    open Space
    @вҷӯ О“ : Type (lsuc (рқ“ҳ вҠ” рқ“Ө вҠ” рқ“Ҙ))
    О“ = ОЈ[ A вҲ¶ Space рқ“Ө ] (A .Carrier вҶ’ Space рқ“Ҙ)

    @вҷӯ ПҖО“ : О“ вҶ’ Type (рқ“Ө вҠ” рқ“Ҙ)
    ПҖО“ О“ = ОЈ (О“ .fst .Carrier) (Carrier вҲҳ О“ .snd)

    @вҷӯ П• : (x : О”В№ вҶ’ О“) вҶ’ is-covariant (О» i вҶ’ ОЈ (x i .fst .Carrier) (Carrier вҲҳ x i .snd))
    П• x = ОЈ-is-covariant
            {B = Carrier вҲҳ fst вҲҳ x}
            {C = О» i a вҶ’ x i .snd a .Carrier}
            (UFib-is-fib (fst вҲҳ x))
            (UFib-is-fib (uncurry (snd вҲҳ x)))

    @вҷӯ П•МӮ : О  О“ (вҲҡбөҲ(О» a вҶ’ is-covariant (О» i вҶ’ ОЈ (a i .fst .Carrier) (Carrier вҲҳ a i .snd))))
    П•МӮ = Оөвҷӯ (rintro (modвҷӯ П•))

    need : (x : О“) вҶ’ is-acov (ОЈ (x .fst .Carrier) (Carrier вҲҳ x .snd))
    need x = вҲҡбөҲ-naturalityвҶҗ is-covariant _ x (П•МӮ x)

instance
  ОЈ-Is-acov
    : вҲҖ {@вҷӯ рқ“Ө рқ“Ҙ} {A : Type рқ“Ө} {B : A вҶ’ Type рқ“Ҙ}
      вҶ’ вҰғ _ : is-acov A вҰ„ вҰғ _ : вҲҖ {a} вҶ’ is-acov (B a) вҰ„
      вҶ’ is-acov (ОЈ A B)
  ОЈ-Is-acov = ОЈ-is-acov auto! (О» _ вҶ’ auto!)

opaque
